{"type": "article", "id": 47565, "title": "杜蕾斯给一堆品牌写感谢信，6 秒广告越来越火 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2017-11-24T04:21:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 17934, "name": "感恩节"}, {"id": 5095, "name": "滴滴"}, {"id": 7221, "name": "杜蕾斯"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 38, "praise_count": 201, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171124112915rQvCbMHajnBGhR0c.gif", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">又是代言</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.cnxz.cn/news/201711/23/359196.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>法国皮具品牌 Longchamp 宣布女演员春夏担任中国区形象大使</b></a>。2015 年时，春夏凭借电影《踏血寻梅》获得“第19届富川国际奇幻电影节”最佳女主角奖。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124114446H1lViWGsM5gUD8qK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/11/24/wuqilong-encounters-with-kiwi-above-the-air/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>新西兰航空（Air New Zealand）以国鸟几维鸟的视角拍摄的创意广告，吴奇隆作为品牌挚友在片中出镜</b></a>。这是新西兰航空首次将全球品牌活动“飞享·新西兰”带入亚洲市场，中国成为这一全球品牌活动的第一站。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=k0508o4v6ud&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的案例</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 38.0px; font: 38.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #4d4f52; -webkit-text-stroke: #4d4f52} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 38.0px; font: 38.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #4d4f52; -webkit-text-stroke: #4d4f52; min-height: 50.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/brand-marketing/apples-holiday-ad-just-dropped-and-its-as-enchanting-as-youd-expect/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>苹果发布了 2017 圣诞广告，名字叫 Sway（摇摆）</b></a>：女主角在大雪天塞着 Airpods 听歌，撞到了男主角，两个人一起起舞。背景音乐是 Sam Smith 新专辑的曲目 Palace。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=j0508cnbwar&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"http://news.adidas.com/US/Latest-News/ALL/adidas--calling-all-creators-/s/3cfa8c28-bfcf-4c53-a3bb-ff7d000df613\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>阿迪达斯发布新广告 Calling All Creators</b></a>，呼叫创造者，暗搓搓夸了观众一句。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124115357S987vphNZKmRVlHe.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.537500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/24130.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>杜蕾斯感恩节营销，给宜家、德芙、Levi's 等一堆品牌写了感谢信</b></a>，绿箭还回信了。文案水平是真的稳定。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124115928pR2aSIJlYHgC7hTO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.466667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711241159396KfcYOMRaeWLIiwT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.466667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124115951QvEHndqDLhWfjclG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.466667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124120000LDzpbkI2i60fAyoG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.466667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124120006Wv74ledckHpKnLJO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.462319\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124120014pTnkMsbxA2cWGH5e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.462319\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/11/23/regarding-a-car-as-a-boat-this-driver-helps-one-old-woman-and-wants-to-be-a-ferryman/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>滴滴上线品牌广告，“以车为舟，摆渡悲喜”</b></a>，讲了一个城市深夜故事，表达每个滴滴司机都是城市里的“摆渡人”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=y0508cvejpy&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>最后，也挺重要</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/t-mobile-finds-success-with-six-second-ads-2017-11\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>6 秒广告越来越火，最近现身说法的是美国 Fox 电视台</b></a>。他们在 2017 年世界棒球职业大赛期间投放了 T-Mobile 的 6 秒广告，并说这是他们“今年目前为止最成功的营销活动”。</p><p>Fox 传媒集团广告销售执行副总裁 Bruce Lefkowitz 说，6 秒广告采用了 15 秒广告的定价策略，“我们正在减少广告时长，目标是利用 54 秒的中断时间产生以往需要 135 秒来达到的广告收益。”</p><p class=\"\">题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/11/23/the-recent-transcript-of-6-second-tv-spot-is-from-the-advertiser/\" rel=\"nofollow\">madisonboom</a></p>"}